Help for MVAPICH:

1. Ulimit -l: This value should be large (Unlimited)
For this, 
vim /etc/security/limits.conf

##add the following line to all your nodes

<username>  hard memlock unlimited
<username>  soft memlock unlimited

## now reboot the system



2. Using RoCE: use the following command:
  $ mpirun -env MV2_SMP_USE_CMA=0 -env MV2_USE_RoCE=1 -np 8 ./a.out

-env MV2_DEBUG_SHOW_BACKTRACE=2 : Provides verbose error messages

